{"tid":703190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑叫同袍注資　 受騙警燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-06-15T13:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T16:22:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d80829c93f72b7528eaba789abb119fe13c55b9a","tid":703190,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180615/20421101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F20421101&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZiS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=84313915\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F20421101&h=3a9c81ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180615/20421101</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月15日 <br />\n<br />\n疑叫同袍注資　<br />\n受騙警燒炭亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180615/large/15la7p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180615%2Flarge%2F15la7p3.jpg&h=40f0842e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員伍銘建去年7月初燒炭自殺，屍體由仵工移走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為了成功騙取金錢供自己花費，警嫂朱凱欣極盡吹噓，聲稱自己是明星保母，又以能賺取豐厚利潤為餌，誘騙多名熟人投入大量資金，加入成炒賣兵團。她不但向女兒就讀幼稚園的同學家長和老師埋手，連警隊中人亦相繼中招受騙，其中交通警伍銘建除自己投資外，亦疑幫忙游說其他同袍注資，在騙局爆煲後，伍因承受不了困擾而自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n伍銘建加入警隊約20年，與妻育有兩名子女。據知伍亦是本案的受害者之一，被騙數十萬元。警嫂夫婦於2013年案件被揭破後遭拘控，伍則一直情緒不穩，更患抑鬱，並搬離寓所。他曾被列為本案證人，但於去年7月審訊前夕，被發現於獨居的工廈劏房燒炭自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有家長失近660萬元<br />\n<br />\n案中受害者「大戶」要數警嫂女兒同學的家長曹淑晶，她與警嫂感情不錯，因聽信對方炒賣手袋可大賺，注資1,400多萬元，最後損失近660萬元。一心打算炒賣愛馬仕手袋和Chanel產品賺大錢的還包括警嫂女兒的老師，<br />\n她除自己炒外，還介紹兩名同行投資，其中一人鄰居聽說可半價買Chanel亦付錢，不過最後貨銀兩失。警嫂也曾向女兒學校的一對姊妹家長借錢，聲稱叔父在澳門賭錢輸了100萬元，兩人借出共10萬元，但她遲遲未還錢，幾經追討卻開出兩張空頭支票。<br />\n<br />\n■記者蔡少玲  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n與夫靠炒勞騙局過奢華生活　 警嫂重囚6年3月<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n普通話婦庭內拍照被捕"},{"pid":"8b18c34ac209db865ce815b12d9cc4ee4b8ea155","tid":703190,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e28e71b1dd0ec9676dfd10d4792af8b400c6f5","tid":703190,"uid":34189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"呢排都賺夠啦,我都想比其他人賺下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50253a40b179c8ef1465294cd32e4cb173555371","tid":703190,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有請小鳳姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e482bf0cf83574fd6d0732a8b369aebc93a2a80","tid":703190,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"係咪借貴利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c4846433c472afafc28f9301cd937c908330f9","tid":703190,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66fbcba01ad6a4406eaeed4e6d07ed36368bcb7","tid":70